  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>To avoid confusion: The top option is the game, the lower option is the <strong>standalone</strong> OST (which does NOT include the game).</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search <i>Keyboard Warrior: Dreamstate Prologue</i> to try the game for free.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076850/extras/24364254f9b092aeddad28c96f0f2cc8.avif?t=1736731533\" width=460 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weave through enemies and collect crystals to stay alive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your character(s) with round-based and meta progression systems to mix and match load-outs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076850/extras/63e39a32ee1a0f4c4ace0d4593a80d79.webp?t=1736731533\" width=30 height=23 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076850/extras/5130a705561164dd192803ee59cc1237.webp?t=1736731533\" width=30 height=23 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076850/extras/62759cf756bd26ae0d764f4a19297d95.webp?t=1736731533\" width=30 height=23 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076850/extras/d7569163e3d2f878645eb6b6e36f3b6a.webp?t=1736731533\" width=30 height=23 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076850/extras/8171e4ffa0e55179b76997a62c4bd5a1.webp?t=1736731533\" width=30 height=23 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle through swarms of hungry geometry to emerge victorious. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076850/extras/5ad8cd3e43cdb5d6a7967e721be21ad1.avif?t=1736731533\" width=64 height=64 /></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076850/extras/48e52c51b51865f14ef8b43ce8f752e6.avif?t=1736731533\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or don't. It's up to you.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>To avoid confusion: The top option is the game, the lower option is the <strong>standalone</strong> OST (which does NOT include the game).</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search <i>Keyboard Warrior: Dreamstate Prologue</i> to try the game for free.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076850/extras/24364254f9b092aeddad28c96f0f2cc8.avif?t=1736731533\" width=460 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weave through enemies and collect crystals to stay alive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your character(s) with round-based and meta progression systems to mix and match load-outs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076850/extras/63e39a32ee1a0f4c4ace0d4593a80d79.webp?t=1736731533\" width=30 height=23 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076850/extras/5130a705561164dd192803ee59cc1237.webp?t=1736731533\" width=30 height=23 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076850/extras/62759cf756bd26ae0d764f4a19297d95.webp?t=1736731533\" width=30 height=23 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076850/extras/d7569163e3d2f878645eb6b6e36f3b6a.webp?t=1736731533\" width=30 height=23 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai